@753 = ~Mental Control~
@754 = ~Mental Control (Enchantment)
Level: 5
Range: visual range of the caster
Duration: 3 rounds + 1 round/2 levels
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: negates

The warlord who casts this spell tries to control the actions of the target.
If the latter fails a saving throw vs. spells at -4, will go under the control of the warlord and follows his orders. They can turn against his own, but still keeps a minimum of lucidity: if the warlord of any member of the party tries to harm him, he will immediately put an end to the spell.
But if the creature is fairly low or unlucky to miss the saving throw without penalty, the bond created by the spell is much stronger. In such a case, the control over the creature is full, so the latter will not react if a party member tries to harm it, and only a successful dispelling or expiration of the spell will free it from the clutches of the wizard.
This spell can only control humanoid creatures. The mental bound is telepathic, there is no barrier of language and culture to prevent it.~
