@7512 = ~Invisibility (Illusion/Phantasm)
Level: 5
Range: 0
Duration: 5 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: the caster
Saving Throw: none

This spell causes the warlord to vanish from sight and be undetectable by normal vision or even infravision. Of course, the invisible creature is not magically silenced, and certain other conditions can render the warlord detectable. Even allies cannot see the invisible creature or his gear, unless these allies can normally see invisible things or employ magic to do so. Items dropped or put down by the invisible creature become visible, items picked up disappear if tucked into the clothing or pouches worn by the warlord.
As long as he is invisible, he can not be targeted, and only creatures that actively tries to look for him have a chance to spot him. If he comes to be spotted, any aggressor attacks him with a -4 bonus to attack. He also gains a +4 bonus to saving throws.
The mage stays invisible throughtout the duration of the spell, unless dispelled or a powerful divination spell negates it.~
